run: Waxay ka dhigan tahay qiimaha macquulka ah ee 1 ama 'on'
been ah: Waxay ka dhigan tahay qiimaha macquulka ah ee 0 ama 'off'
maaha: Hawlwadeen macquul ah oo beddela qiimaha runta ee odhaahda
iyo: Hawlwadeen macquul ah, run kaliya haddii labada tibaaxood run yihiin
ama: Hawlwadeen macquul ah, run haddii ugu yaraan hal odhaah run tahay
xor: Gaar ah AMA, run haddii dhab ahaan hal tibaax run tahay
miiska runta: Jadwalka muujinaya wax-soo-saarka dhammaan isku-darka wax-soo-gelinta ee odhaahda boolean
khilaafid: Hadal boolean ah oo had iyo jeer been abuur ah
sharciyada de Morgan: Xeerarka lagu maamulayo tibaaxaha booleeyada ee MAYA, IYO, iyo AMA
bayaan shuruudaysan: Waxay xakameysaa fulinta koodka iyadoo ku saleysan in xaaladdu run tahay iyo in kale
naand: MA iyo - run kaliya haddii labada tibaaxood ay been yihiin
sidoo kale: MA ama - run kaliya haddii labada tibaaxood ay been yihiin
aljebrada boolean: Nidaamka xisaabeed ee loo adeegsaday qaabaynta iyo falanqaynta caqliga boolean
